# Focus

P a-p Productivity Language

===================================================================================

# Routine Tasks

## Daily Routines
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

P Run 3 km = Done(21/12/13 Sat) //dates are in day/month/year + name format 
P Study at Treehouse = Done(21/12/13 Sat)

# Weekly Routines
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

W Check "In Box" = due(mon-fri) Done(20/12/13 fri) //this task is due monday to friday
C Prepare Intercession =due(sun) ToDo(16/12/13 mon) //I'd better hurry up

===================================================================================
# Reminders

## Short Term

W 26/12/2013 Thu - Remind A. Smith if(TaskA, !Done)	//! is a negation so !Done = "Not Done"
C 26/12/2013 Thu - Remind P. Morales if(TaskB, !Done)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## Long Term

W 16/01/2014 Thu 17:00 - Attend Webinar, see Email/Webinar Confirmation: The Platform for Building Great Software
P 03/02/2014 Mon - Remind B. Wolzniak, if(Payment Rent, !Done)
===================================================================================

