# Key 

P Personal

C Church

W Work

Due(date) Deadline
Done(date) This bit was done 

Wait(someone, something, date) 
    This bit is waiting for someone to do something since "date". 
    "Someone" defaults to self, "something" defaults to "bits above", date should never be missing)

